VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT request\.GET
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(execute|raw\(|extra\(|eval\(|subprocess|os\.system|redirect|HttpResponse|mark_safe|safe_filter) && MISSING:(escape|sanitize|validate|cleaned_data|get_validators)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of request.GET, which may contain untrusted inputs.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Inputs: request.GET.
